Version 0.3-0
 
   *  Auto-generated bindings for many of the routines in the API

   *  cuGetContext() tests for NULL value of external ptr value, not the object.

Version 0.2-0

   *  copyFromDevice() a generic

   *  .cuda() (and alias .gpu()) will copy R vectors to the device and back

   *  .cuda() has an outputs parameter to control what is copied back from the GPU
      and returned.

   *  Documentation for the exported objects

   *  Package's profiler configuration file used by default.



   